{"tid":1290544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［急！］搵仔谷想起文宣底","createTime":"2019-07-06T13:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T04:26:28.000Z","uid":20058,"like":100,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"f81b709c7f461f45387d2da04a881191ee147354","tid":1290544,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"[安全提醒]搵仔谷想起文宣底，本 Channel 係度提少少安全提醒俾文宣人士：<br />\n1. 唔好用電郵收圖或者文宣材料<br />\n電腦比手提電話好 hack 好多，Attachment 裡面夾嘢好容易就中伏。所以請文宣轉 Telegram 收材料。<br />\n2. 注意材料 Metadata<br />\nWord、PDF 等務必將 Author、Editor 等資訊清理之後再 send。<br />\nPSD 及其他相片資料，請移除 EXIF 等資訊再進行發送。<br />\n3. 電腦進行 Hard Disk Encrypt<br />\n將所有處理材料嘅電腦，進行硬碟加密，我哋會儘快出 Post 跟進如何加密。臨時措施，可使用 7-Zip 或 WinRAR 等，將文件加 Password 之後再保存。"},{"pid":"2e30d1f71231f2ab3b193bdda6f1d2cc9d11bfb4","tid":1290544,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35022d6099f6b86e586c1c24a81b08571b46758c","tid":1290544,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3e6ef86a381572421eef39134459858d9f34d6","tid":1290544,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"4d5e1d8530b3840cd92344797baf90ced2426fae","tid":1290544,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"66131dbd593ac00479934426ad59f38a0ef61b2d","tid":1290544,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a19cd613380d779258250def5b616251f42fa6e9","tid":1290544,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9e99cd11942f27aac26dd15e1dfce8ad2523a54","tid":1290544,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cited